  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/f897a15d1bd4ce1e2f920f20dfdbca3b.poster.avif?t=1593074009\" width=640 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/f897a15d1bd4ce1e2f920f20dfdbca3b.webm?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/f897a15d1bd4ce1e2f920f20dfdbca3b.mp4?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Online Co-op Action Roguelike</u></strong><br>Team up with your friends or go solo to take on the dungeons in this open world top down action roguelike.<br><br>The world is procedurally generated every time you play, and the items are randomized. Offering a unique experience with each play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a99a8fcf1585b7c3ed0575975d5510fc.poster.avif?t=1593074009\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a99a8fcf1585b7c3ed0575975d5510fc.webm?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a99a8fcf1585b7c3ed0575975d5510fc.mp4?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Voxel Destruction</u></strong><br>Everything in the dungeons are made of cubes, and can easily be reduced back to them as well!<br><br>Watch out for traps and monsters as you delve deeper looking for loot.<br><br>The dungeons are fully destructible, can't find your way out of a room? Blow a way out with your bombs!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a8b9f4dabdaba62ee76631e8c503c48c.poster.avif?t=1593074009\" width=640 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a8b9f4dabdaba62ee76631e8c503c48c.webm?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a8b9f4dabdaba62ee76631e8c503c48c.mp4?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Custom characters / skin editor</u></strong><br>Create your own character with the simple to use in-game voxel editor.<br><br>You can even re-skin the monsters, items, and textures too!<br><br>Once you're done making a character set or skin pack, share it on the workshop for all to use.<br><br>----<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Custom characters</strong><br></li><li><strong>Online Multiplayer</strong><br></li><li><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong><br></li><li><strong>Procedural Dungeons & Randomized items</strong><br></li><li><strong>Retro Overworld to explore</strong><br></li><li><strong>3D Guidebook that keeps track of your goals</strong><br></li><li><strong>Custom items/monsters/dungeons skins</strong><br></li><li><strong>Workshop support for sharing characters/skins</strong><br></li><li><strong>Classic Bosses</strong><br></li><li><strong>Awesome music by hyperunknown</strong><br></li><li><strong>Real time combat inspried by Zelda and beat 'em up games</strong><br></li><li><strong>Permadeath</strong><br></li><li><strong>Voxel destruction</strong><br></li><li><strong>Cooperative gameplay</strong><br></li><li><strong>Controller support</strong><br></li><li><strong>Framerate, 60/120/144 FPS or unlocked</strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/f897a15d1bd4ce1e2f920f20dfdbca3b.poster.avif?t=1593074009\" width=640 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/f897a15d1bd4ce1e2f920f20dfdbca3b.webm?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/f897a15d1bd4ce1e2f920f20dfdbca3b.mp4?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Online Co-op Action Roguelike</u></strong><br>Team up with your friends or go solo to take on the dungeons in this open world top down action roguelike.<br><br>The world is procedurally generated every time you play, and the items are randomized. Offering a unique experience with each play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a99a8fcf1585b7c3ed0575975d5510fc.poster.avif?t=1593074009\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a99a8fcf1585b7c3ed0575975d5510fc.webm?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a99a8fcf1585b7c3ed0575975d5510fc.mp4?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Voxel Destruction</u></strong><br>Everything in the dungeons are made of cubes, and can easily be reduced back to them as well!<br><br>Watch out for traps and monsters as you delve deeper looking for loot.<br><br>The dungeons are fully destructible, can't find your way out of a room? Blow a way out with your bombs!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a8b9f4dabdaba62ee76631e8c503c48c.poster.avif?t=1593074009\" width=640 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a8b9f4dabdaba62ee76631e8c503c48c.webm?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/375810/extras/a8b9f4dabdaba62ee76631e8c503c48c.mp4?t=1593074009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Custom characters / skin editor</u></strong><br>Create your own character with the simple to use in-game voxel editor.<br><br>You can even re-skin the monsters, items, and textures too!<br><br>Once you're done making a character set or skin pack, share it on the workshop for all to use.<br><br>----<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Custom characters</strong><br></li><li><strong>Online Multiplayer</strong><br></li><li><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong><br></li><li><strong>Procedural Dungeons & Randomized items</strong><br></li><li><strong>Retro Overworld to explore</strong><br></li><li><strong>3D Guidebook that keeps track of your goals</strong><br></li><li><strong>Custom items/monsters/dungeons skins</strong><br></li><li><strong>Workshop support for sharing characters/skins</strong><br></li><li><strong>Classic Bosses</strong><br></li><li><strong>Awesome music by hyperunknown</strong><br></li><li><strong>Real time combat inspried by Zelda and beat 'em up games</strong><br></li><li><strong>Permadeath</strong><br></li><li><strong>Voxel destruction</strong><br></li><li><strong>Cooperative gameplay</strong><br></li><li><strong>Controller support</strong><br></li><li><strong>Framerate, 60/120/144 FPS or unlocked</strong></li></ul>",
